episodes.title: From Cult Control to Real Estate Closings and Healing Women!
episodes.description:
In this episode, I sit down with Megan Bingman, a former cult member turned powerhouse realtor and trauma-informed physical therapist. Megan shares her gripping story of growing up in a community where women were expected to submit, stay small, and cover their heads. But her soul always knew she was meant for more.

Now on her way to earning a doctorate, Megan is helping others heal through her work as a realtor.  

If you are enjoying this podcast, please help up spread the word by sharing it!
